4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper models player behavior in two ways, which may involve machine learning techniques, making cs.LG a possible sub-category. 
5. cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper proposes a solution using publicly-announced information, which may involve information theory concepts, making cs.IT a possible sub-category.
